

**Mash g Melkisedekbad d kownal ch d ep pahl **

1 Nt wo haꞌichu em‑ahgi ab amjed hegai Melkisedekbad mant wo em‑tashogi g Jesus chikpan. Jiosh atsh am i kei g Melkisedekbad. Kush d kownal am Salem kihhim ch ed ch d ep pahl. 

Kutsh idam Abrahambad gam hu hebai gidahiop k am haꞌi ha kokda g pi apꞌekam kokownal k ab uhpam hihim. Kutsh g Melkisedekbad ab ha nam k ab i s‑hoꞌigeꞌel g Abrahambad am wehhejed g Jiosh. 2 Tsh g Abrahambad ab mah mo haschu ab d wuikamaj g Jiosh mash d hemako tahpna mo wehst‑mahm e tahpanch g gehgewadaj. 

Melkisedekbad chehgig o hab d ahga ‘S‑apꞌekam Kownal.’ K g Salem hab d ahga ‘Dodolimadag.’ K heg hekaj d ep dodolimkam kownal. 3 Pi o an hu hebai oꞌohanas mas hedai d ha‑amjedkam g Melkisedekbad ch has masma mahsi k has masma heb hu hih. K id am t‑chehgidch mat has masma in wo i wuhsh g Jiosh alidag ab dahm kahchim t amjed k am uhpam ep wo him k d wo uhgchu pahlk chum hekid. 

4 Melkisedekbad oki baꞌich d i si s‑has haꞌichu mo g Abrahambad. Tsh heg ab mah g hemako tahpna mo wehst‑mahm e tahpanch g gehgewadaj matsh am ui cheggiadag ed 5 K hab chuꞌig g t‑chehanig matsh hegam t‑wehm oꞌodham mo d Levibad amjedkam ch d papal ab t‑amjed wo ui hegai hemako tahpna matsh wehst‑mahm wo e tahpanch g t‑gehgewadag. 6 Kush ihda Melkisedekbad pi d Levibad amjedkam. Tsh eda g Abrahambad ab namkid hegai mo d Jiosh wuikam. Tsh g Melkisedekbad ab i s‑hoꞌigeꞌel. 7 Kuch s‑mahch mat g geꞌechu ab wo s‑hoꞌigeꞌel g chumchu. K heg hekaj baꞌich i geꞌej g Melkisedekbad mo g Abrahambad. 

8 Melkisedekbad o baꞌich d i si s‑has haꞌichu mo g t‑papalig. Hegam o wabsh koꞌihim. K wabshaba pi an hu hebai oꞌohanas mat muh g Melkisedekbad. 9 K heg wa wepo mat g t‑papalig ha‑shohshonbad Levi am namkid g Melkisedekbad 10 nash pi ab d Abrahambad amjedkam mash heg am namkid. 11 Jiosh atsh am i ha chuhcha g Levibad amjedkam matsh d wo t‑papaligk ch ab wo t‑mah g chehanigaj. T wabshaba pi wo shaꞌi e nako g t‑papalig mas am wo i t‑apꞌech g Jiosh wehhejed. Tsh heg hekaj ab hema ep i wuhsh mash gawul masma mo hegam ch wepo masma g Melkisedekbad. 12 Kut hemho wa am gawul juh g Jiosh g e‑chehanig mat am wo i kei g Jesus mat d wo t‑pahligk. 13-14 Heg ash pi ab hu d Levibad amjedkam ch wabshaba ab d Judabad amjedkam matsh idam pi d wo chum papalk am t‑chehanig ed. K heg hekaj tasho mat g Jiosh am gawul juh g e‑chehanig am t‑wehhejed. 

**Matsh g Jesus am i e kei hab masma matsh wa g Melkisedekbad **

15 Neh, baꞌich ant am wo i em‑tashogi mo g Jesus pi ha wepo masma g t‑papalig ch wabshaba wepo masma g Melkisedekbad. 16 Pi atsh e pahlch g t‑chehanigkaj k wabshaba e pahlch g gewkdajkaj g e‑doakag. K g doakaj d pi ha huhugedam. 

17 Heg o hekaj ab amjed oꞌohanas mash ab wui hab kaij g Jiosh: 

Am ant i m‑kei hab masma mant wa am i kei g Melkisedekbad. 

Kupt chum hekid d wo uhgchu pahlk. *Psalm 110:4 * 

Neh, bo kaij g Jiosh am e‑alidag wui. 

18-19 Kut heg am i t‑apꞌech Jiosh tahgio mach ab hahawa s‑ap miabid. Heki hu t‑chehanig o pi ab hu shaꞌi t‑mahkch g gewkdag machs hekaj am wo i t‑apꞌech Jiosh wehhejed. Kut hekaj g Jiosh gam hu hab i juh. 

20 Jiosh ash hab wabsh kaij matsh g Levibad amjedkam d wo papalk 21 ch wabshaba g e‑gewkdagkaj hab kaij ab wui g Jesus: 

Ahni ani g ni‑gewkdagkaj hab si kaij mapt d wo uhgchu pahlk chum hekid. 

Kunt pi hekid am gawul wo juh g hab ni‑elida. *Psalm 110:4 * 

Neh, bash kaij g Jiosh. 22 K id am t‑chehgidch mat g Jiosh am i apꞌech g baꞌich i s‑kehg apꞌechuda mat hi heki hu nat pi am i kei g hejel e‑alidag mat d wo uhgchu pahlk chum hekid. 

23 Hegam Levibad amjedkam at pi wo e nako mas d wo papalk chum hekid no pi koꞌihim. 24 T wabshaba g Jesus chum hekid d wo doakamk. T hab pi hedai ep am kehkud ed wo i kekiwua. 25 Kut wo e nako mat wehs wo ha doꞌibia hegam mat am gahi wuhshanim ab wo i e nohnogi Jiosh wui nat pi chum hekid d wo doakamk ch am ha wehhejed ab wo tahnid g Jiosh mat am wo i ha wehmt. 

26 Tatchua ach g si s‑ap uhgchu pahl. K g Jesus woho hab masma ch d hekia s‑apꞌekam ch i e gawulkadch ab ha amjed g pi apꞌekam. Idani o an daha Jiosh wehm an dahm kahchim ch ed. 27 Pi o wepo masma hegam mo d uꞌugchu papal am heki hu t‑chehanig ed. \(a\) Hegam o d pi ap chuꞌijkam ch wehpeg ab wo haꞌichu iagchul hejel e‑chuꞌijig wehhejed k ab haha wo iagchul g hemajkam ha‑chuꞌijig wehhejed. K wabshaba g Jesus pi ha chuꞌijig. \(b\) Hegam o chum hekid ab haꞌichu iagchulid Jiosh wui. T wabshaba g Jesus hemho hab juh. T heg wehs am i apꞌech g pi ap ha‑chuꞌijig. \(c\) Hegam o ab haꞌichu chum namkid g Jiosh. T wabshaba g Jesus hejel am i e dagito mat hekaj ab wo iagchul. 28 Hegam mo d papal ab heki hu t‑chehanig wecho o pi d shaꞌi hekiakam ch pi ap wo nahto g e‑chikpan. T wabshaba g Jiosh am hahawa i kei g e‑alidag g hejel e‑gewkdagkaj. K heg d uhgchu t‑pahlig ch d si hekiakam. Pi at hekid wo huhug g gewkdaj. T hab s‑ap wo nahto g e‑chikpan. 

